<div class="main-content">

<h2>Help & User Guide</h2>
<hr>

<h4>System Modules</h4>

<ul>
<li><b>Master Module</b> – Manage Cane, Cultivator, Harvestor, Vehicle, Transporter, Village, Water</li>

<li><b>Information Module</b> – Register cultivator cane details</li>

<li><b>Transaction Module</b> – Cane Cut Slip and Weight Slip entries</li>

<li><b>Reports</b> – Generate reports for cultivators, registration, cane cut, and weight slips</li>
</ul>

<h4>How To Use</h4>

<ol>
<li>Create Master data (Cultivator, Vehicle, etc.)</li>
<li>Register Cane</li>
<li>Create Cane Cut Slip</li>
<li>Add Weight Slip</li>
<li>View Reports</li>
</ol>

<p>If you face any issue, contact system administrator.</p>

